To give you a bit more context, when a game is newly launched, as a UX designer, you only

172
00:08:06,926 --> 00:08:10,910
want the most important call to actions to be presented, because you don't want to

173
00:08:11,091 --> 00:08:13,193
overwhelm the player or create a choice bias.

