00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:31,980
These could be the daily reward systems,

183
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,101
your alliance systems, help requests,

184
00:08:34,221 --> 00:08:35,322
special offers, and so on.

185
00:08:36,202 --> 00:08:38,423
So it is very much possible that this information,

186
00:08:38,563 --> 00:08:39,843
that a new event is available,

187
00:08:40,063 --> 00:08:41,944
might be getting drowned in that noise.

188
00:08:44,172 --> 00:08:47,936
Now if the player clicks on the event icon, somehow, he'll come to screen number two.

