210
00:09:57,042 --> 00:09:57,122
it?

211
00:09:57,803 --> 00:09:59,284
And second, what is the risk involved?

212
00:10:00,225 --> 00:10:01,946
What are my chances of getting that reward?

213
00:10:02,507 --> 00:10:04,648
And that is what comes through by looking at the leaderboard.

214
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:09,402
Now it is possible that at any given point of time,

215
00:10:10,363 --> 00:10:12,705
we may have three to four events running in parallel.

216
00:10:12,985 --> 00:10:15,407
Let's say daily, weekly, monthly,

217
